cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about super-resolution using convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which is a topic related to computer vision (CV) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper proposes a new structure to avoid checkerboard artifacts, which is a technical contribution related to artificial intelligence (AI) and neural networks (NE). Finally, the paper presents experimental results, which is a topic related to multimedia (MM).
